<br>
And, if you WTB an item, and I send you a tell asking &quot;How much you paying?&quot;  It's because I have that item equipped or it's in the bank.  So don't ask me to set a price, Offer me what you were willing to pay for it.  9 times of 10 that's more then I thought it was worth anyway.<br>
